ActPublic Service Employment Act
PrecisAppointment of SHAHID MINTO of Ottawa, Ontario, to the position of special adviser to the Minister of Public Works and Government Services to be known as Procurement Ombudsman Designate, to hold office during pleasure, until such time as the Procurement Ombudsman is appointed, effective September 10, 2007.
